        "setup": "In the Polar dashboard, open your organization [Settings](https://polar.sh/to/dashboard/settings), scroll to **Developers**, click **New Token**, then choose a name, expiration date, and scopes. Use the token as `Authorization: Bearer <token>`. Create separate tokens for production and sandbox because the environments are isolated.",
